declarations.comments:
`..` is a synonym for `<<<` for aesthetic reasons.

`foo .. bar .. baz` looks and reads better than `foo <<< bar <<< baz`,
and mimics accessor notation for records.
A valid `Lens` satisfies all three of the following laws.
declarations.title: validLens

declarations.comments:
If you get a value out, and then set it immediately back,
nothing should change.
declarations.title: getSet

declarations.comments:
If you set a value, and them get it immediately out,
you should get the value you set.
declarations.title: setGet

declarations.comments: If you set two values, the last set is the one that matters.
declarations.title: setSet
